------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Variables can simply be replaced with actual values by wrapping them into some
curly braces, like this: {{ variable }}. Whitespaces don't matter.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1 = {{ v1 }}, v2 = {{v2}}, v3 = {{       v3               }}.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{"v1": 123, "v2": "{{x}}", "v3": "yeah"}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1 = 123, v2 = {{x}}, v3 = yeah.
